   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Harpokration, strategos of the ;Arsinoite (nome), Herakleidou meris, ;from Dios, son of Didymos and ;Kronion, son of Diogenes and the ;remaining sitologi of the village of ;Philadelphia. We have had measured out to us, ;on the 8th of the present month ;Pachon of the current 21st year, as receipts of the 20th year artabai [; to the account of Marcus Valerius [; at this point the papyrus has been brocken off</ab>
         </div>
